nodes.text: The Winagrew system was a planetary system in the Graador sector in the Mid Rim at Galactic coordinates J-17. Around 1 ABY, Alliance to Restore the Republic leader Leia Organa was supposed to visit the system on a diplomatic mission, but was captured by rogue Imperial Commander Rezi Soresh before she could arrive.
The Winagrew system received a mention in Alex Wheeler's 2010 novel Rebel Force: Uprising.
